@node "Object Info" "LED Object Information"
AFLed/Object Information

  The Led Object was written to provide a C++ Object Class interface to the Led BOOPSI object.  Initial values for
the led object are set to zeros with the default number of digit pairs set to one.  Other defaults for this class
are:
  Colon - TRUE
  Negative - FALSE
  Signed - TRUE
@endnode

