@node "Create" "Create"
AFLed/Create

  NAME Create(AFWindow *window, AFRect *rect, ULONG id)

  DESCRIPTION
    This funtction adds the Led BOOPSI object to a window

  INPUTS
    window - window to which object is to be added
    rect - coordinates and size of object
    id - gadget id of object (not yet supported)

  RESULT
    TRUE if successful
    FALSE if failure

  BUGS
    none known

  SEE ALSO
@endnode

@node "RemoveObject" "RemoveObject"
AFLed/RemoveObject

  NAME RemoveObject()

  DESCRIPTION
    This funtction removes the Led BOOPSI object from the window to which it was added

  INPUTS
    none

  RESULT
    LONG - position in the glist from which the object was removed
    FALSE - if failure to remove object

  BUGS
    none known

  SEE ALSO
@endnode

